{"tid":1528547,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"回港航班大延誤 滯台客：嬲警察多過抗爭者","createTime":"2019-09-01T14:21:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T14:21:49.000Z","uid":68738,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"99665137efdd49b90db62205549a6d7b0bbb420c","tid":1528547,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T14:21:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190901/large/1567343136_0517.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190901%2Flarge%2F1567343136_0517.png&h=f330e14a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n滯台港客王小姐：「我嬲香港警察多過（抗爭者）阻住我返屋企，警方要交代番噚晚（太子站）件事先。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190901/large/1567343147_09b3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190901%2Flarge%2F1567343147_09b3.jpg&h=e35f09d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n滯台港客王小姐見到大批港人滯留桃園機場。受訪者提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n網民今日（1日）發起「和你塞」行動，香港旅客王小姐晚上約7時半抵達台灣桃園機場，原訂乘搭9時半的航班返港，但抵達機場離境大堂時，已見到大批香港旅客滯留。她稱，航空公司地勤人員建議她改飛其他地方，她隨即向地勤人員查詢香港國際機場是否已關閉，「佢話唔係，但就話晏晝曾經閂過香港機場，仲話下午3點幾班機啲客仲未走到，建議我唔好飛入去（香港）。」<br />\n<br />\n她又稱，航空公司的地勤人員未有解釋航班未能起飛的原因，只着她留在離境大堂等候，不要出境，「否則清關好麻煩」。她對於網民發起「和你塞」表示理解，「雖然航班可能受影響，但可以理解，我都係遲一日返香港，我嬲香港警察多過（抗爭者）阻住我返屋企，警方要交代番噚晚（太子站）件事先。」<br />\n<br />\n此外，也有香港旅客下午一度已在台北上機準備返港，但客機未能起飛，機組人員就廣播指香港國際機場暫時不允許客機起飛。另有旅客原定乘搭中華航空6時半的航班返港，初時被通知航班要延遲到明天起飛，但其後更將有關航班已取消。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190901/59999078?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190901%2F59999078%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=3Z9ZeYaQzwHPi2iIp4702Fu%2BYei5PLor89YqF%2FSdhCs%3D&h=4e7234d5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190901%2F59999078%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=04361538\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190901/59999078?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"}]}